data.description: Charming 3 bedroom, 2 bath one level home in peaceful Gordon Lakes with no HOA. Open floor plan with large eat-in kitchen featuring stained cabinets, custom backsplash, and pantry with views into the family room. The primary suite features a bay window/perfect sitting area, while the bath features double vanities and a soaking tub. There is engineered hardwood floors in the great room, natural light throughout. A second full bath ensures guests will have privacy when visiting. This home is close to shopping, restaurants and recreation in Villa Rica and easy access to 1-20. With a 2 car garage and a large fenced in back yard, you will have plenty of space for gatherings and a place to enjoy quiet evenings on the porch. Schedule your private showing today!
